eventRemarks: TS Mar. 2022: This 'station' is what Martin Stein called SINGLETON305. I just changed to name to something more descriptive.
occurrenceRemarks: MKB05: Was not found. MKB05: The holotype is a female from June 28, the two paratypes are from June 29 and July 3, all Sagami Sea, Mortensen 1914. TS Mar. 2012: The paratypes mentioned by MKB05 have not been found in the lot. Type status checked 2003-2011, but may need reconfirmation. Labelled with correct number Mar. 2012.
